des: WLPO continues its 75+ year heritage of providing the Illinois Valley and Starved Rock Country with local news, weather & sports. Rod & Tom start weekdays just after 5:30 a.m. with the latest news & talk. After 10 a.m. WLPO offers news and weather updates with top hosts Clare & Jeremy playing Starved Rock's best classic rock. Weeknights and weekends feature local high school sports in season and just the right amount of news mixed with more rock and great memories on shows like Time Warp.
